Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised myself that I'd give him a good punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Ivica.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife, Eureka, saved my life once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you describe the state she's currently in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you familiar with the anthropic principle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sci-fi idea that reality changes based on who the observer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub Coral is an intelligent unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:01:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To escape the Limit of Questions, they found a means to travel between universes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you call the Quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Different universes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, not the future, but an entirely different universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Coralian, Eureka must've turned herself into Quartz,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and took the dangerous Quartz with her to somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've only desired to be \Ntransported to a {\i1}different{\i0} time and place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she couldn't arrive or \Nmaterialize at a particular destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something? Isn't that what you're here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to save Mom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You destroyed the Scub for that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been reported that the Quartz Gun's power could alter the course of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Quartz Gun is a large collection of Quartz that has taken the form of a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it can change time and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be one more shot left in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been looking for it, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Eureka gave birth to Ao on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ten years since Mom disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing this entire time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years? Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:03:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, it was just a short while ago that she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A short while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Thurston, what does that—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man who just appeared might be another threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should strengthen our surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Ao's father and Eureka's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka and the Gekko arrived here before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we discovered that the Scub that came to this universe went back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It traveled from the distant future of this Earth to countless pasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Quartz opened the door to parallel worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world considered that as a danger, and as a result, Secrets emerged naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to survive, the Scub desired to go somewhere without Secrets:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the past of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Secrets chased them through the holes in time that the Scub opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus came the history of Scub Bursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the future, mankind became extinct due to Scub Bursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, the Secrets considered us enemies as well and attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down, Eureka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renton?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:06:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go to another time through the Scub's pillar of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere with less trapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Renton?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy all the Scub here. Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make you destroy Scub!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renton... Renton!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renton! Renton! Renton! Renton! Renton!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RENTON!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the distant past, Eureka gave birth to you and tried to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renton... I mean, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying so hard to destroy the Scub?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our responsibility as adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Responsibility as adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time when we fought to protect the Scub Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Naru said Mom's the same as the Scub.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we protected it that this \Nuniverse has to suffer from Scub Bursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Thurston!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to ten thousand years in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Are you going to abandon Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Nirvash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, I must go after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I still think Dad's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults shouldn't do stuff that they'd have to apologize to kids for!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot the first Scub Coral in this universe with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub Coral will then be erased from all past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, I want to return this universe to its correct form!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only fire it once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mom then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka's prepared for it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit! I can't lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fighting back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That movement...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! The Neo should have no Archetype!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, Ao! Follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell am I hearing Truth's voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I've been with you this entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Archetypes wish to help LFO pilots that need us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awaiting your orders, Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Archetype... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth was once a Secret, but in this world changed by the Quartz Gun, he exists as an Archetype.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth, is this the one and only truth? Or the truth you desired?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you mumbling about, Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why's there an Archetype in that machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, get out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One Nirvash with an Archetype is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The original's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Says who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Quartz Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere, Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked before if you had a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bringing that up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka told me about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She turned into stone right after she was born and passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:12:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a high trapar density environment, the different types of cells in a child of a human and a Coralian reject each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how corals die, the child turns into rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you chose this world... this \NEarth that Mom discovered by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to raise your second child in a traparless world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's Scub Coral here too, so you tried to erase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went so far to keep me alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a dear friend... A dear friend who's also a Coral Carrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lives in symbiosis with the Scub!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Scub gets erased from this world, what is going to happen to all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they've merged with the Scub, they might disappear along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erasing something that's wrong doesn't make it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man called Blanc told me to look for what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he meant the right enemies that aren't Secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for an enemy means we still have to fight in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't live on this planet with the way your body—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up on this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though a child's life is young, it's still life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to negate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fake it just because it's more convenient to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Okinawan pole light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad arrived from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, what do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he wants to enter the pole light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go save your mom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?! You said we're family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still want your real family then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, so you were lying to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Fleur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring an end to all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save Mom, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to shoulder this alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, you're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The emotions of intelligent creatures make the Quartz resonate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the burst ten years ago! Take me to where my Mom is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't do. I have to take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao! Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know it's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point in time, I should be only two years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, you told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I accidentally arrived here in the Gekko,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you showed up in your Nirvash and helped me return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was piloting that Nirvash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came for me, Renton!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? You were over there just then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why "Mom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. And goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then understood that I'll be giving birth to you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy named Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Dad knew my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did, you wouldn't have believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were pregnant with my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renton!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go with Dad, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave the Quartz here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been hard for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had to fight and kill the Scub, your own kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone once told me that I was selfish to have fallen in love with Renton and have a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we must take responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something or someone must be sacrificed for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break free from that curse already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's the reason why I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for you, I don't care how much hardship I must endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renton, don't cry in front of Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dad, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... We'll somehow manage in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why at the very least I want to send you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows how long my body will last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll believe in the future my parents chose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that we, the people of this time and this planet, chose and worked for!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are my parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm so glad both of you made it back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth, where are we this time around?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I'm investigating right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go. It's year 2027.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Year 2027.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You changed the world three times with the Quartz Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the world you know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Ao may not even \Nexist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, no one will remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved your mother, then said goodbye to her forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wandered in time for a long while,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that might not be a big deal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had to live in a place she didn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gave birth to me all alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and had to endure solitude just to keep me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to what she had to go through, this much is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do, Truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's not over for me yet in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, we'll meet again somewhere.
